[[SideEditor|$:/plugins/TWaddle/SideEditor]] floats a tiddlers editor by the story river side.

Thus you see the changes //live// in the tiddler and you can scroll to, and reference, stuff from other tiddlers while you edit.

;Usage
*''Activate'' it via the tiddler tool button <span class="about-icon">{{$:/core/images/right-arrow}}</span>
*''Re-size'' it via the "handle bars" at upper-right and lower-left corner.
*''Switch focus'' between //Sidebar, River// and //SideEditor// by ''hovering''.

;Note!
:Specifically [[macros|A macro]] are not //live// updated. Instead the changes take effect when<br> the SideEditor <span class="about-icon">{{$:/core/images/done-button}}</span> is clicked to close the editor.

''Installation'' - grab, drag and drop the link $:/plugins/TWaddle/SideEditor into your TW.

